rows.label: tlk44300184_01_msg0001
rows.name:
It's the same exact scene every time,
but still I keep coming here...

rows.label: tlk44300184_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My shop used to be on this street.
It's long gone now, though...

rows.label: tlk44300184_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I sold Luxurian wares, but then supply
became a problem, prices went
soaring...

rows.label: tlk44300184_01_msg0004
rows.name:
And then when the black market
started up... I went bust. Now my life
depends on that same black market...
